    dc:creator "Shima, Hiroshi; Abe, Tomokazu; Libra, Martin" ;
    dc:date "2021" ;
    dc:title "Tachinid flies (Diptera: Tachinidae) reared from deciduous plant-feeding lepidopteran larvae at Hokkaido University Tomakomai Forest (Japan), with descriptions of three new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5627318>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5627320>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5627330> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5627318>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. Adult males of Blepharomyia spp. 1, 3, 5. Habitus in lateral view. 2, 4, 6. Head in lateral view. 1–2. Blepharomyia brevicornis sp. nov. (paratype, Hokkaido, Japan). 3–4. Blepharomyia foliacea Mesnil (Hokkaido, Japan). 5–6. Blepharomyia pagana (Meigen) (Germany)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5627318/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5627320>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–12. Male and female terminalia of Blepharomyia brevicornis sp. nov. (paratypes, Hokkaido, Japan). 7. Male 5th abdominal sternite in ventral view (hairs omitted on left side). 8. Epandrium, cerci and surstylus in dorsal view (hairs omitted). 9. Same in lateral view (hairs omitted on epandrium and cercus). 10. Hypandrium, pregonite, postgonite and phallus in lateral view. 11. Female terminalia in lateral view. 12. Same in ventral view (hairs omitted). Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5627320/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5627330>
    dc:description "FIGURES 35–44. Puparia. 35–36. Blepharomyia brevicornis sp. nov. (paratype, Hokkaido, Japan). 37–38. Ctenophorinia grisea Mesnil (Hokkaido, Japan). 39–40. Cyzenis equifacialis sp. nov. (paratype, Hokkaido, Japan). 41–42. Cyzenis tetrasetosa sp. nov. (paratype, Hokkaido, Japan). 43.44. Eulasiona zimini Mesnil (Hokkaido, Japan). 35, 37, 39, 41, 43. Lateral view. 36, 38, 40, 44. Posterior apex in lateral or posterior view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5627330/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

